{"tid":736114,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"BBC：劉霞正飛往柏林","createTime":"2018-07-10T04:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-12T15:37:10.000Z","uid":41404,"like":152,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"6b7d6e1d4caa8eebbd264a8b91eba05db28940a7","tid":736114,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"本周五（13日）是諾貝爾和平奬得主劉曉波逝世一周年。英國廣播公司(BBC)報道，據數名了解情況的消息人士透露，劉曉波的遺孀劉霞，剛剛乘坐由北京飛往柏林的芬蘭航空班機離開北京。其胞弟劉暉仍在北京。<br />\n<br />\n7月10日，北京時間上午11時許，劉曉波遺孀劉霞離開北京，前往柏林。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180710/58423601\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F58423601&d=rE3B90NEQHXNPJOAwJx82%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=1e3f6202\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180710%2F58423601&h=0fcb7850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180710/58423601</a>"},{"pid":"250967860d02bb51b8bb454ebf825a90a63bfc8e","tid":736114,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"137db068491f3602f5e345aef5779ec249aee563","tid":736114,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:21:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2fc1365a6d81524279fbd0b187e5e77122791c0","tid":736114,"uid":55309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"4b1205cc9522820f6abd688be68350d03272e2cc","tid":736114,"uid":3028,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T04:24:22.000Z","msg":"放得走應該就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71367b59f6d2995afbb73d40e5e94d7ed7f53552","tid":736114,"uid":102096